Package RestaurantSim.SimulationSystem

  • Interface Summary
    Interface Description
    IEvaluationService
    An interface that defines how object of Restaurant class should be evaluated
    IOrderQualityDeterminer
    An interface that defines how order quality should be determined (calculated)
    IOrderRater
    An interface that defines how order should be rated.
    ITickableActionFinishCallback
    An interface that defines a behavior of a TickableAction when it is finished.
    ITickableActionObject
    Classes that want to use TickableAction objects must implement this interface in order to be properly registered and processed.
    ITickableActionTickCallback
    An interface that defines a behaviour when TickableAction is updated (which happens every tick).
    OutputDisplayProvider
    An interface that provides methods to print any kind of information in form of Strings.
